Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.88,0:41:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Some animals have even learned to be intelligent,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.65,0:41:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,have really learned how to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.05,0:41:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,utilize the frontal cortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.23,0:42:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You see Alex and Coco
