Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.65,0:42:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,all these people on all these
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.44,0:42:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,continents and all these countries
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.07,0:42:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.90,0:42:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,These people will booby trap you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.55,0:42:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and blow off your legs with a landmine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.50,0:42:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And Coco will merely
