Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.63,0:42:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,this is light and this is dark, but they're both blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.59,0:42:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So it takes training
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.59,0:42:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to train him. Light blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.69,0:42:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,dark blue. Oh. I don't know
