Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.19,0:43:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,TV, but he's out of the University of Arizona.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.86,0:43:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.63,0:43:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that's enough of the slides
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.59,0:43:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,for today. So, what I want
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.84,0:43:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to retract is the evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.92,0:43:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness throughout all
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.00,0:43:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of the eons.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.59,0:43:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's evolution through the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.26,0:43:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.82,0:43:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Our inheritance
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.61,0:43:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of it is so obvious, I mean, you've
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.82,0:43:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,laid it out in spades
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.48,0:43:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,for anybody to see
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.19,0:43:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that the evolution of your ego
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.44,0:43:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is the evolution of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.26,0:43:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,nature itself, its expression
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.23,0:43:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is life, and its qualities
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.40,0:43:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,are critical and essential to
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.11,0:43:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,survival. Consequently,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.15,0:43:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you can stop feeling guilty about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.92,0:43:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can see how
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.25,0:43:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the inner instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.69,0:43:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,grab intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.96,0:43:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and education and begin
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.94,0:43:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.38,0:43:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Utilize it towards its own end.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.07,0:43:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's where spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.32,0:43:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness and commitment and teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.21,0:43:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.17,0:44:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We also showed
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.26,0:44:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,at the last lecture how
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.71,0:44:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,now, with the beginning of, once you get
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.15,0:44:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,over consciousness level 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.03,0:44:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,then love
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.80,0:44:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in its various forms and
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.46,0:44:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,utilization of intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.19,0:44:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in the interest of love
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.36,0:44:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes more and more
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.53,0:44:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,powerful. And eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.90,0:44:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it begins to change brain function.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.07,0:44:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we show that at the last lecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.94,0:44:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How? Brain function?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.36,0:44:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? We had the brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.36,0:44:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Alright. So you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.75,0:44:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,see, the likelihood of the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.75,0:44:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,mind and the intellect reaching truth
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.75,0:44:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is extremely slim. I'm writing
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.23,0:44:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,about it right now, and I
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.84,0:44:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,thought, how do we ever get to know the truth about
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.84,0:44:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,anything? It looks
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.84,0:44:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,almost impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.84,0:44:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason is
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.15,0:44:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,because spiritual intention
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.15,0:44:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,then comes forth as a radiation,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.15,0:44:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,like the radiance of a new energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.88,0:44:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.88,0:44:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are attracted to
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.88,0:45:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and we follow that field.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.88,0:45:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And thereby transcend our
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.88,0:45:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,identification with the animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.88,0:45:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't really get rid of
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.94,0:45:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a thing until you own it. You can't
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.13,0:45:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,get rid of an addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.13,0:45:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you admit that
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.28,0:45:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's got you. So,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.80,0:45:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't get rid of the ego by denying
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.80,0:45:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it, by demonizing
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.80,0:45:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it, by making it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.80,0:45:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,our enemy, but by
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.32,0:45:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,owning it and beginning to see
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.32,0:45:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and appreciate it and respecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.32,0:45:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful mechanism
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.57,0:45:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,without which life wouldn't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.57,0:45:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Without which there wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.05,0:45:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,be any Komodo dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.23,0:45:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're one of the great wonders of the modern world.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.23,0:45:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's this dragon from
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.28,0:45:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,four million
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.28,0:45:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,BC still with us in the zoo
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.28,0:45:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,or wherever they keep Komodo dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.28,0:45:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they live in Indonesia
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.28,0:45:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,on a little island there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.03,0:45:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a wonderment. So we can
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.03,0:45:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,wonder at the evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.03,0:45:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of the animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.03,0:46:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I would now tell people
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.61,0:46:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,give your ego a name, something
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.61,0:46:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can own, that it's
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.61,0:46:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,my Fuzzy. And of course Fuzzy
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.63,0:46:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you hate them. Of course Fuzzy
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.63,0:46:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.32,0:46:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course Fuzzy you want it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.71,0:46:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course Fuzzy you want to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.71,0:46:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He deserves it, don't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.92,0:46:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you begin to own. As you own
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.92,0:46:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,then you don't have to be in denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.92,0:46:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to project it on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.92,0:46:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When you own it yourself, you stop
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.92,0:46:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing other people as evil and
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.92,0:46:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that they're caught in the same
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.92,0:46:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,animal way of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.92,0:46:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're caught
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.19,0:46:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in the same evolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.59,0:46:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,evolutionary stall out
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.59,0:46:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of the brain. They're caught
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.32,0:46:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in the same trap. Happily
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.36,0:46:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you've seen the light and have learned
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.36,0:46:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,how to move beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.73,0:46:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is a transition period
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.73,0:46:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,where you go through
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.86,0:46:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a difficulty in confronting
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.86,0:46:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.86,0:46:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because before that you project
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.86,0:47:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it onto others or you deny it or
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.86,0:47:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you project it onto God or somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.86,0:47:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you have to own it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.59,0:47:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can own it if you see it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.59,0:47:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so you contextualize
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.59,0:47:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.59,0:47:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason to appreciate it, I spend
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.59,0:47:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so much time on the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.59,0:47:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is because when you really and
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.59,0:47:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,completely and totally understand it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.59,0:47:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it loses its power over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.59,0:47:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lost its power to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.01,0:47:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,really know the truth of that which it is
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.01,0:47:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and how it got to be that way
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.01,0:47:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you can say
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.01,0:47:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,good old Fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.01,0:47:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you want all the cookies on the plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.01,0:47:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you want to drown your little
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.40,0:47:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,sister in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.76,0:47:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Edie Wibletree
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.90,0:47:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,drowned her playmate in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.90,0:47:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother looked quite grave and said then
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.90,0:47:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Edie, don't do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.90,0:47:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see my little pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.90,0:47:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got your tootsies wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.44,0:48:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Edie Wibletree
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.07,0:48:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,wants to drown her playmate in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.07,0:48:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She hates her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.76,0:48:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So we respect our animal
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.03,0:48:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution. We stop
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.03,0:48:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,glorifying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.03,0:48:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If the universe is created by divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.03,0:48:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,then that's how it
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.03,0:48:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,unfolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.25,0:48:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We are serving some purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.25,0:48:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to connect this evolutionary
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.25,0:48:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,line with
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.28,0:48:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,a life that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.05,0:48:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,takes over on a non-physical
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.05,0:48:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,level.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.42,0:48:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The devotion to truth then.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.42,0:48:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.61,0:48:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is nothing but one's biologic
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.61,0:48:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,ancestry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.28,0:48:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It lives on in the very
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.28,0:48:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,structure and anatomy
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.28,0:48:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of the human brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.92,0:48:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Without it you wouldn't even be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.51,0:48:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can give it credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.01,0:49:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for good old ego
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.05,0:49:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be standing here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.82,0:49:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.15,0:49:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual energy which also
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.15,0:49:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,surrounds humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.15,0:49:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to pull us even beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.15,0:49:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And we begin to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.15,0:49:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't there something more?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.80,0:49:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there something better?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.80,0:49:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want you to be aware
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.80,0:49:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that the ego is not
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.80,0:49:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,adhering to any religion whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.98,0:49:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And never even mentioning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.98,0:49:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessary to mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.55,0:49:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As you let go now
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.55,0:49:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is the animal
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.94,0:49:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,if you didn't understand anything about the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.94,0:49:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just told you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.94,0:49:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the human mind is not at the service
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.94,0:49:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to the animal
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.94,0:49:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and you become a student of your own mind
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.94,0:49:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and get a little notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.94,0:49:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and you notice what your animal did today
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.94,0:49:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,what it did today
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.98,0:49:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you become
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.98,0:49:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a psychologist by here
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.98,0:49:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,being a student of your own nature
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.98,0:50:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,how it shines forth
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.01,0:50:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and how it shines forth in everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.01,0:50:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't have to be
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.01,0:50:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,secret, it doesn't have to be mystical
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.01,0:50:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't have to be
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.42,0:50:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,couched in foreign languages
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.42,0:50:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to pull it out of antiquity
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.42,0:50:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's observable
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.88,0:50:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,rediscoverable right now
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.88,0:50:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in the immediate present.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.61,0:50:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin to own it for what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.61,0:50:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin surrendering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.61,0:50:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.80,0:50:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as it comes up
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.11,0:50:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you can forgive it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.11,0:50:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you can let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.76,0:50:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you can let go wanting to control it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.76,0:50:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,there are all the mechanisms
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.11,0:50:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that all the various schools and workshops
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.11,0:50:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,teach various mechanisms
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.21,0:50:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,meditation and contemplation
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.84,0:50:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and the one that I
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.84,0:50:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,recommend because
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.84,0:50:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it's unstoppable
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.19,0:50:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is contemplation
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.19,0:50:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,meditation you see
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.19,0:51:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you gotta sort of take yourself out of it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.19,0:51:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and go someplace
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.40,0:51:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,like it and give yourself tendinitis
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.40,0:51:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.67,0:51:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you know every orthopedist says
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.67,0:51:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,practicing meditation eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.67,0:51:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,knees twisted up
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.86,0:51:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,your back all warped out
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.51,0:51:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so people will take a course
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.51,0:51:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,on meditation become intensely involved
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.51,0:51:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in a weekend workshop
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.51,0:51:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and be with some teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.59,0:51:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,etc and then
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.59,0:51:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you visit them again in Chicago three years later
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.59,0:51:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and they've given it up long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.59,0:51:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,why is that? Because
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.59,0:51:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you gotta take time out from real life
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.59,0:51:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say real life
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.59,0:51:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.61,0:51:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and you just don't have time to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.61,0:51:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for the same reason you gave up playing
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.61,0:51:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Parcheesi years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.61,0:51:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you just haven't got time to get out
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.67,0:51:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the game board and go someplace
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.67,0:51:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and say you wanna play Parcheesi
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.76,0:52:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,eh? Chinese marbles
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.61,0:52:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever it was
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.61,0:52:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was gonna say scruple
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.63,0:52:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,scrapple what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.71,0:52:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in my childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.65,0:52:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it was called scruple not scrapple
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.65,0:52:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,scruples
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.67,0:52:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,scrupulous
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.51,0:52:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,scrapless
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.78,0:52:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so we don't have time to take out
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.78,0:52:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so we skip it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.03,0:52:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore a contemplative way
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.03,0:52:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of being in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.51,0:52:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,when you get to consciousness level 500
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.51,0:52:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,this happens anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.71,0:52:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,one just begins
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.71,0:52:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to appreciate more and more
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.71,0:52:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the beauty of life
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.71,0:52:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,one becomes sensitized to beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.71,0:52:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and beauty itself is one of the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.71,0:52:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,pathways to God
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.32,0:52:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the virtue of one's spiritual commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.32,0:52:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.00,0:52:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you open doors
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.00,0:53:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,experiential doors
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.00,0:53:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and the progression of experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.00,0:53:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that would not have occurred
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.00,0:53:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,had you not made that commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.11,0:53:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to be spiritually committed
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.11,0:53:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is to automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.11,0:53:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,bring into your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.11,0:53:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,into your existence
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.11,0:53:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,into your experience of your own existence
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.11,0:53:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,things sequencing
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.30,0:53:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.50,0:53:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in a way that would not have happened otherwise
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.50,0:53:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,doors open
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.50,0:53:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that wouldn't have opened
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.50,0:53:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you say I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.50,0:53:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,just I got there and the door opened
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.82,0:53:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.03,0:53:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.65,0:53:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,call it miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.65,0:53:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but that again is going in the other direction
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.65,0:53:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.75,0:53:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.75,0:53:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's what's normal
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.78,0:53:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that's reality for a spiritually committed person
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.78,0:53:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,things should work out
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.94,0:53:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,one should uncover new sources of joy
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.07,0:53:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,these are all part and parcel
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.07,0:53:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore spiritual commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.15,0:54:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,pulls into you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.15,0:54:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,a field
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.19,0:54:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the field then begins to support you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.19,0:54:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.36,0:54:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.36,0:54:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's nothing special
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.36,0:54:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the automatic consequence of the field
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.11,0:54:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,an ocean without salt
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.11,0:54:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,has different buoyancy
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.25,0:54:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,than an ocean with salt
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.25,0:54:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,all you've done is add tremendous salt
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.25,0:54:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you're more buoyant than you were before
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.25,0:54:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so you float higher
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.59,0:54:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,as a consequence of your spiritual commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.82,0:54:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course you think differently
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.82,0:54:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you see things differently
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.82,0:54:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because spiritual commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.01,0:54:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically changes brain function
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.01,0:54:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it changes brain function
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.01,0:54:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it automatically creates an etheric brain
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.11,0:54:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,one now has an instrument
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.11,0:54:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,through which all experience is
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.15,0:54:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,filtered or processed
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.15,0:54:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,which is not present
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.15,0:54:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Komodo Dragon doesn't have an etheric brain
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.15,0:54:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,he doesn't really worry about things
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.03,0:54:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,lucky from a certain viewpoint right
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.67,0:55:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,lucky Komodo Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.28,0:55:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate and give reverence
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.28,0:55:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to our own spiritual nature
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.28,0:55:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have owned it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.28,0:55:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and acknowledged it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.11,0:55:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and in so doing
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.11,0:55:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,we have benefited all of mankind forever
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.11,0:55:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,a group like this
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.73,0:55:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,by merely owning
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.76,0:55:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality of your own spiritual power
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.76,0:55:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and truth
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.30,0:55:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,changes the consciousness of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.53,0:55:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,changes the consciousness of mankind forever
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.53,0:55:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,changes the consciousness of mankind forever
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.80,0:55:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,not disconnected from it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.57,0:55:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because you are the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.57,0:55:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite field
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.15,0:55:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is here present
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.30,0:55:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,within all of us
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.30,0:55:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and as we move our spiritual commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.82,0:55:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to the field
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.82,0:56:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the field itself becomes more powerfully influential
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.82,0:56:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of us
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.11,0:56:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.42,0:56:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because of each and every one of us
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.42,0:56:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,each and every one of us benefits
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.42,0:56:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I benefit by you sitting right there
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.42,0:56:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I benefit by you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.42,0:56:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,every single person here
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.46,0:56:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we all enormously radiate
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.46,0:56:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,enormous power
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.46,0:56:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to each other
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.00,0:56:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,which I never speak of
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.00,0:56:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but today I thought I would
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.19,0:56:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a fact
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.48,0:56:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we are all moving along
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.48,0:56:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,not just as a consequence of our
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.48,0:56:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,being so wonderful ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.48,0:56:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but the fact that we are surrounded by people
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.48,0:56:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,who are wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.84,0:56:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and we are included in their field
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.84,0:56:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so all of life benefits
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.05,0:56:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and by our commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.40,0:56:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and we automatically bring the miraculous
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.40,0:56:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,into our life
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.40,0:56:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as the everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.44,0:56:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,things
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.76,0:56:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when other people drop a button
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.76,0:56:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,from the bureau
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.44,0:57:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't find it
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.44,0:57:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.92,0:57:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to have that button
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.92,0:57:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you find it
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.01,0:57:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you think everybody does that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.01,0:57:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,no they don't
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.01,0:57:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't find the button
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.48,0:57:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,if it wasn't for the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.55,0:57:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we would never find our cat
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.55,0:57:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,he keeps getting lost
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.55,0:57:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we have staff in and out
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.55,0:57:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and the office is attached to the house
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.55,0:57:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so we have to have that button
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.40,0:57:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,thus far
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.40,0:57:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy Spirit has answered every prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.40,0:57:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask God
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.40,0:57:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,where is the kitty
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.51,0:57:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and the next thing you move over
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.51,0:57:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and there underneath the pillow
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.51,0:57:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a little tail sticking out
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.30,0:57:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is the kitty
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.30,0:57:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want us to really appreciate ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.82,0:57:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,for this holiday season
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.07,0:58:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and it should be nameless of course
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.53,0:58:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,because this lecture could be heard by others
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.67,0:58:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in this bleep season
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.96,0:58:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.96,0:58:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the day of the rising
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.05,0:58:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it just increases our awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.05,0:58:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence of love
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.05,0:58:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as a prevailing quality
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.05,0:58:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of all of life
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.05,0:58:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to see it in all that exists
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.44,0:58:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it appears as beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.44,0:58:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,stillness
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.19,0:58:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,silence
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.19,0:58:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,going over the mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.76,0:58:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,yesterday the snow
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.76,0:58:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and the divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.80,0:58:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you just see the divinity of
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.80,0:58:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,expressing itself as existence
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.80,0:59:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in that beauty of this incredible form
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.42,0:59:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when we go out
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.42,0:59:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,coming to your restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.42,0:59:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and we begin calibrating
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.55,0:59:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese fortune cookies
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.55,0:59:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,did I mention them to you
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.13,0:59:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,yes or no
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.13,0:59:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.13,0:59:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.13,0:59:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,oh
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.13,0:59:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,well I lecture in various places
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.63,0:59:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess this was in
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.28,0:59:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,where are we in California
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.50,0:59:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and Пượcка
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.50,0:59:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you know everybody's worrying about truth
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.50,0:59:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I say truth is
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.50,0:59:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that if you have the capacity to see it, we found that Chinese fortune cookies calibrate around 350.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.17,0:59:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you look at one, for the first time you begin to really look at one,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.53,0:59:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see something like, a kind thought can change your life forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.78,0:59:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.76,1:00:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,One kind thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.48,1:00:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They calibrate Chinese fortune cookies calibrate at 350.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.53,1:00:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A single kind word will keep one warm for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.21,1:00:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, will come to you by mail.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.96,1:00:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This side's in Chinese. I can't read it. Oh, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.86,1:00:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You have at your command the wisdom of the ages.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.50,1:00:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As you begin looking at Chinese fortune cookies, we calibrated them generically, they calibrate at 350,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.69,1:00:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which beats a large proportion of the world's
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.51,1:00:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,literature and spiritual literature.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.86,1:01:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if you would just read Chinese fortune cookies.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.32,1:01:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now tell him, he said, what should I do to become enlightened?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.69,1:01:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is what you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.65,1:01:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me in 20 years, tell me how it worked out. To be kind at all times,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.19,1:01:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to be kind at all times towards all of life and all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.71,1:01:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need anything more than that? No, because as you are,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.96,1:01:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it begins to change its occurrence to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.40,1:01:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you thought was just a dumb animal, you see, is the radiance of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.26,1:01:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I use that word, the radiance of the source of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.82,1:02:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,One Chinese fortune cookie, you do it consistently as a way of being is all kind of read anything,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.94,1:02:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,do anything, go anywhere. You just do that as a way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.59,1:02:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So contemplation is owning a reality,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.59,1:02:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it alters the way you are. To be kind towards all things,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.11,1:02:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,transforms all of life. Is that what it's saying? To see the truth of it, and it shines for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.19,1:02:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And you make it your way of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.05,1:02:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it your way of life. And as you do that, everything around you begins to get transformed.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.98,1:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything around you seems to change.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.42,1:02:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is our wish. That's my present to you for this coming holiday season.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.84,1:03:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Chinese fortune cookie, fortune, which has the power to transform all of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.32,1:03:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll take a break and then we'll just do questions and answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.51,1:03:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't run a fortune cookie.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.19,1:03:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Different format today, we set up everything differently, the microphones, the cameras.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.05,1:04:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we'll have people come up and sit here and we can have a dialogue, discuss things.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.84,1:04:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, we have questions that are already presented on cards.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.80,1:04:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll try to answer them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.38,1:04:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll try to answer everything as best we can, or at least I'll give you my response to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.94,1:04:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My response to it, which may not be the answer that you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.63,1:04:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll give you the response.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.63,1:04:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them ask technical questions, the answer to which I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.36,1:04:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're not too relevant anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.59,1:04:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll try to sort out the relevant from the irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.11,1:04:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the mind likes to think in terms of content.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.23,1:04:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.09,1:04:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,which is in the 400s, with the prevailing energy, which brings us all here,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.90,1:04:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is because we're all articulate, we all read, we follow reason and logic.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.36,1:05:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And we pretty much mastered, mastered in the operational sense, the mind and the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.13,1:05:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we're interested in what is beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.80,1:05:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind and the intellect will examine how it sort of developed over time in the next lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.80,1:05:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.03,1:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated all.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.67,1:05:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The great books of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.19,1:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Every contributor to the great books of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.51,1:05:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The greatest intellects that have ever lived.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.76,1:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But that'll be next.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.05,1:05:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll track where the intellect can take us.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.53,1:05:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, the intellect thinks up questions and we'll try to answer them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.71,1:05:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What can a group like this, this is one of the cards, do to raise the consciousness of mankind?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.28,1:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I explained this morning, we've already done it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.25,1:05:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.65,1:05:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.65,1:05:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.13,1:05:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The collective intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.73,1:05:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To raise consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.07,1:05:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not our intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.36,1:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we don't all take up spiritual work in order to raise the consciousness level of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.44,1:06:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's not your province.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.36,1:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave that for the Avatar.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.88,1:06:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the Avatar is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.30,1:06:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's his responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.82,1:06:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You worry about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.23,1:06:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcend the level of the hippopotamus.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.67,1:06:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To be kindly and loving towards all things.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.90,1:06:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To follow that Chinese fortune cookie will take you the whole way.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.05,1:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.48,1:06:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one opens the door to the next revelation.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.61,1:06:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And the next revelation, you move from that level and that takes you to the next revolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.17,1:06:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,See, once you begin opening the doors, they open up their own.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.98,1:06:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you do that, you collapse the wave function.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.30,1:06:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a question, what does that mean, collapse the wave function?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.84,1:06:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There, on the internet, Henry Stapp, S-T-A-P-P, professor out of Berkeley, advanced theoretical
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.65,1:06:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,physics.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.21,1:06:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Does about as good a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.73,1:07:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He explained it, you know, from the potentiality, which is the Schrodinger equations, time dependent
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.67,1:07:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and time independent, then arises.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.59,1:07:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the state of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.59,1:07:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the state of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.11,1:07:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Any condition of the universe is obviously potentially the source of the next stage,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.03,1:07:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.59,1:07:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that there I'm here, I can decipher this with the Schrodinger equations, it now
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.36,1:07:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,has a potential.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.07,1:07:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,By exercise.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.28,1:07:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,By exercise of the Heisenberg principle of observation, and especially that of intention,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.40,1:07:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I now potentiate the potential to an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.07,1:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I have a new state of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.48,1:07:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've collapsed the wave function.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.48,1:07:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, to mathematically discover what's happened to my arm, you need the Dirac equations.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.63,1:07:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All that happens through the von Neumann process, process one and process two.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.19,1:07:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're interested in that, read it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.88,1:08:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very interesting stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.07,1:08:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Very interesting stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.11,1:08:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need it, but it's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.36,1:08:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I'm telling you how to transcend mind, and now I'm giving you all this mind fodder.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.88,1:08:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving me a guilt panic thing here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.53,1:08:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.27,1:08:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the reason I like to bring those things in is because you don't have to desert intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.92,1:08:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, one objection of the atheist is he has to transcend confirmable, verifiable truth
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.72,1:08:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and go to that ooh-la-la stuff, all that ooh-ooh-ooh stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.47,1:08:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the director of a big clinic, not too far from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.09,1:08:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And any time many of the staff wanted to bring any kind of spirituality, he'd go,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.85,1:08:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,all that ooh-ooh-ooh stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.85,1:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all that ooh-ooh-ooh stuff has stopped the greatest intellects of history.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.26,1:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Isaac Newton at 499, Sigmund Freud at 499, Albert Einstein at 499.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.15,1:09:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is a great barrier.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.23,1:09:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And my job as a teacher is really how to
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.35,1:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,contextualize things so that the transcendence of the intellect becomes an automatic consequence
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.60,1:09:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of the process itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.73,1:09:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the intellect is the great trap.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.42,1:09:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Very few people get beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.60,1:09:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember from Calvary, love is the consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.77,1:09:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 4% of the world's population ever gets to the level 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.32,1:09:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 4%.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.52,1:09:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's love, which is a different paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.92,1:09:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're moving from the supposedly objective intellect,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.07,1:09:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the world of content, and you're moving to the subjective.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.15,1:09:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So the movement from the describable Newtonian paradigm to the paradigm of spiritual reality
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.43,1:09:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,means you move from the out-there-ness of what you think life is about to the in-here-ness
